      <div class="guia-meta">
        <span>Nivel: inicial</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>Herramienta: Miro (plan gratuito y pagos)</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>Autora: Valeria Yashan</span>
      </div>
    </header>

